==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stroboscope
<hw>Strob"o*scope</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ a
whirling + <ets>-scope</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>An instrument for
studying or observing the successive phases of a periodic or varying
motion by means of light which is periodically interrupted.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>An optical toy similar to the phenakistoscope. See
<er>Phenakistoscope</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Strockle</ent>⟦br⟧
